Title: REST API: support users authenticated via site Apache
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: rest-api
Date: 1610553332
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0b4

When a site's Apache instance is configured to perform authentication,
the there authenticated user is used. This method only works when
a user has already been created in Checkmk.
